                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc" key="work_5842">Mukhtaṣar Buqrāṭ al-ḥakīm fī al-ṭibb</title>
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_5842">مختصر بقراط لحكيم فى الطب</title>
                     <note>Contains Persian and Arabic versions of a medical work on medicine in 67 chapters going under the name of Hippocrates. 1) Persian, ff3-36. 2) Arabic, 39-80. And other works. See notes. Semi-literate notes on ff1a, 80b,117b, 140a refer to the copying of the various sections, and perhaps its composition, among a group of residents of BWNKR including ono or more Lahori physicians in A.H. 1240. Headings, punctuation etc. in red.</note>
